OL,6,FA busy A road is closing for more than
OL,7,Fsix months for repairs after cracks
OL,8,Fstarted to appear.
OL,10,FThe A36 Warminster Road will be fully
OL,11,Fclosed between Limpley Stoke and
OL,12,FMonkton Combe from 12 August until
OL,13,Fspring 2025.
OL,15,FWork is required to stabilise the
OL,16,Fsouthbound embankment following
OL,17,Fcracking in the footpath alongside the
OL,18,Fcarriageway.
OL,20,FThis will prevent further movement and
OL,21,Fkeep the main carriageway safe.
