OL,6,FDuring the closure, National Highways
OL,7,Fwill also make improvements to the
OL,8,Fdrainage to prevent future damage and
OL,9,Freduce the need for more closures.
OL,11,FAll diversion routes have been agreed
OL,12,Fto keep disruption as minimum as
OL,13,Fpossible.
OL,15,FWhile work is carried out, access will
OL,16,Fbe maintained to properties within the
OL,17,Fclosure, with traffic marshals on hand
OL,18,Fto help.
