OL,6,FHugh Campbell, senior project manager
OL,7,Ffor National Highways, said: "Safety
OL,8,Fis our number one priority and we
OL,9,Fapologise for any inconvenience this
OL,10,Fmay cause but need to fix the root of
OL,11,Fthe problem to ensure it doesn't
OL,12,Fhappen again and that motorists and
OL,13,Fpedestrians remain safe at all times.
